Format as for ../emails. Templates are:

  - via-coversheet

    Cover sheet page for fax sent to a representative via another contact
    point, for instance a Democratic Services office.

  - footer-first

  - footer

    Boilerplate footer material appended to, respectively, the first and every
    subsequent page of each fax transmitted. Variables are:

      - this_page, the page number of this page;

      - total_pages, the total number of pages in the fax;

      - representative_url, the URL which a representative may visit to forward
        the fax etc.

  - group 
    
    Template for text prepended to messages sent to a group of representatives. 
    Lets recipients know who the other recipients of the message are. 
